name: No Time Left (Havzp)
description:
Simple game made for the Lame Jam 27, you just have to shoot the enemies, avoid falling off the map and take care of your age, if you reach 0 years or are older than 50 years, you die, maybe I will try to make a better version in the future so any feedback is appreciated

Controls:

WASD: Character Movement, Left Click: Fire
